00:08:34.626 --> 00:08:38.039
And if you just Google
women's soccer Harvard op-ed,

00:08:38.039 --> 00:08:41.280
you'll find it.

00:08:41.280 --> 00:08:44.790
This morning, I think it was,
Bill Littlefield commented

00:08:44.790 --> 00:08:47.740
on their powerful
letter in response

00:08:47.740 --> 00:08:53.920
