00:09:09.660 --> 00:09:12.380
But men, we know
better than that.

00:09:12.380 --> 00:09:15.150
18 years of soccer
taught us that.

00:09:15.150 --> 00:09:19.420
18 years as successful,
powerful, and undeniably

00:09:19.420 --> 00:09:23.400
brilliant female
athletes taught us that."

00:09:23.400 --> 00:09:26.740
And they go on to say, "We're
hopeful that the release

00:09:26.740 --> 00:09:30.130
of this report will lead
to productive conversation

00:09:30.130 --> 00:09:33.500
and action on Harvard's campus
within collegiate athletic

00:09:33.500 --> 00:09:36.780
teams across the country,
and into the locker room that

00:09:36.780 --> 00:09:38.330
is our world."

00:09:38.330 --> 00:09:41.940
