talked about as athletes.

01:31:43.040 --> 01:31:48.170
But I think underneath, even
if it wasn't stated, part of it

01:31:48.170 --> 01:31:52.480
was the appeal of seeing these
incredibly athletic women

01:31:52.480 --> 01:31:53.840
in leotards.

01:31:53.840 --> 01:31:56.440
And I know there was
actually a male gymnast who

01:31:56.440 --> 01:32:02.060
