that was devoted

01:32:20.440 --> 01:32:23.110
to these young
women as athletes,

01:32:23.110 --> 01:32:26.170
underneath that
was a layer of look

01:32:26.170 --> 01:32:28.440
at these women in leotards.

01:32:28.440 --> 01:32:32.050
I think the same thing exists
with volleyball, particularly

01:32:32.050 --> 01:32:33.540
